O que vai ser, George?

366
00:54:31,338 --> 00:54:33,194
Engraçadinhos!

367
00:54:34,251 --> 00:54:36,488
Venha para cá, George.

368
00:54:37,740 --> 00:54:39,917
Senhoras e senhores...

369
00:54:39,916 --> 00:54:42,949
